Perl documentation
==================

This page gives some Perl_ tricks

.. _Perl: http://www.perl.org/

Install perl module dependencies
--------------------------------

Run::

    $ cpan -i $module

i.e::

    $ cpan -i Gtk2

One might need to force the installation (i.e some tests did not pass). To do
this, do::

    $ cpan

Then type::

    force install $module

